1
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,120
An own goal, huh?

2
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:57,959
This...

3
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,120
How could he kick it

4
00:01:59,159 --> 00:02:00,400
into his own goal?

5
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,400
See that?

6
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,319
What a mess.

7
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:02,959
He's a textbook

8
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,239
loser, that's what he is.

9
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,959
And you treat him like a treasure.

10
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,000
What a joke!

11
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:07,719
Are you done yet?

12
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,919
Yaoyao! Yaoyao!

13
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,840
No, that's not what I meant.

14
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,520
I just said he played badly.

15
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,000
Can't you just give it a rest?

16
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,240
Look, Yaoyao's already left.

17
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,840
And there's the whistle,

18
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,400
signaling the end of the match.

19
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,479
Sister Fang,

20
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,479
we'll head back now.

21
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:25,240
Okay.

22
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:28,840
You know what?

23
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:31,719
You really can't blame Xiaoyong.

24
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,800
Look at that play just now,

25
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,120
how dangerous it was.

26
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,599
He was risking life and limb.

27
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,599
Xiaoyong's mom,

28
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,199
I've brewed some medicinal wine.

29
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,599
Have Xiaoyong drink it.

30
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:42,400
It'll give him strength.

31
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:43,919
Okay, thank you.

32
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,120
We'll get going now.

33
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,120
Alright, alright.

34
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,400
Am I wrong?

35
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,360
The things you said,

36
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,680
do you look down on Xiaoyong?

37
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,199
A grown man like him,

38
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,040
no car, no house,

39
00:04:20,319 --> 00:04:21,279
no job either.

40
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,600
Will he ever be able to support

41
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:23,279
your daughter in the future?

42
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,240
A professional career

43
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:25,920
is a narrow bridge to begin with.

44
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:27,959
From now on, use

45
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,160
the grit you showed on the field

46
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:30,920
to face life.

47
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:40,600
Come in.

48
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,000
Have a seat.

49
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,560
Something on your mind?

50
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,199
Coach Chang.

51
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,439
I really appreciate you giving me

52
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,319
this opportunity.

53
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:04,639
I haven't played in a long time.

54
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:08,720
In yesterday's match,

55
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,480
I made a huge mistake.

56
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,240
I don't think I'm cut out

57
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,160
to be the captain anymore.

58
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:20,000
By that logic,

59
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,439
I should resign as coach too.

60
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,920
Coach, that's not it.

61
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,079
The problem is all on me.

62
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:28,920
As a professional player,

63
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:30,360
in such an important match,

64
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:31,360
I made

65
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,319
such a stupid mistake.

66
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:33,439
What does "professional" mean?

67
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:35,319
Without dedication, there's no professional.

68
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,680
What does "amateur" mean?

69
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,680
If you give it everything you've got,

70
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,360
it's not amateur at all.

71
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,000
That goal,

72
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,000
it wasn't your fault.

73
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,120
But we've already

74
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:45,839
lost so many in a row.

75
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,319
Xiaoyong.

76
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,319
What is a captain?

77
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:49,920
A captain is the one who,

78
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:50,959
when everyone else gives up,

79
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:52,360
is the very last one

80
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:54,079
who still believes we can win.

81
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,800
Why did I pick you as captain?

82
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:58,560
Because back then, I saw in you

83
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,519
that refusal to ever back down.

84
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,519
Where did that Xiaoyong go?

85
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:03,800
Are you telling me

86
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:04,759
I misjudged you?

87
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,240
Don't let me see you

88
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,439
looking so dejected.

89
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:08,800
And don't ever let me hear

90
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,800
what you said today again.

91
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:11,920
You be the captain you're supposed to be.

92
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,319
What you should do

93
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,600
is rally all your teammates,

94
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,920
not give up on yourself first.

95
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,240
Losing isn't shameful.

96
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,920
Being afraid to lose is.

97
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:22,079
Whatever burden you carry,

98
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,079
dump it on me.

99
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,279
The sky isn't gonna fall.

100
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,639
What we need to do now is simple.

101
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:28,519
Score one goal.

102
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,680
Just one goal,

103
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:31,600
and it'll boost everyone's confidence.

104
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,480
The Jiangsu Super League

105
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:38,959
is a nationwide sensation now.

106
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,399
The higher-ups are taking it seriously.

107
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,399
So the next match's venue

108
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:45,240
has been changed to the Olympic Center Stadium.

109
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,600
That's a treatment reserved

110
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,759
for national-level competitions.

111
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:50,680
Let me ask you one thing.

112
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:52,800
On the biggest stage

113
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,519
of your life,

114
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,399
do you want to

115
00:07:54,439 --> 00:07:55,800
show what you're truly made of?

116
00:07:59,240 --> 00:07:59,680
Yes.

117
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:06,399
Lao Liu.

118
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,560
You're here too?

119
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:08,560
Lao Chang,

120
00:08:09,199 --> 00:08:10,279
a few friends here

121
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,120
want to share some suggestions with you.

122
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:12,920
Is this a good time?

123
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,639
Of course.

124
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:14,360
Please, come in.

125
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,680
Come, come on in.

126
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,000
Come right in, please.

127
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:18,560
Coach Chang.

128
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:19,079
Coach Li, hello.

129
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,040
Coach Liu.

130
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,399
Hello.

131
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,120
Hello, hello.

132
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:22,120
Coach Chang,

133
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,399
we've watched a few of your games,

134
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,079
and we have some thoughts.

135
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:26,519
Would it be all right

136
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:27,279
to talk them over with you?

137
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,160
Absolutely.

138
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,240
More than all right.

139
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,399
Come on, please sit.

140
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,160
Sit, sit.

141
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:31,759
Have a seat.

142
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,440
Come on.

143
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,399
Let's go.

144
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:41,879
Almost there

145
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:47,840
See that?

146
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,240
This kid's instincts are spot-on.

147
00:08:53,639 --> 00:08:54,519
You really did score one.

148
00:08:59,039 --> 00:08:59,639
Xiaoyong.

149
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:02,879
What is it?

150
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:12,879
Everyone was anxious yesterday.

151
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:15,559
I yelled at everyone on the pitch too.

152
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,320
But nobody meant any of it.

153
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:39,039
My prediction did come true.

154
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,440
Except,

155
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,879
I only got the first half right.

156
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,240
Even though it was a rough opener,

157
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,039
but

158
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:51,320
everyone saw it too.

159
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:54,159
Scoring a goal isn't that hard, right?

160
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:55,600
It's not that hard.

161
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:58,000
Once we score that first goal,

162
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,799
I believe

163
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,120
there'll be a second, a third...

164
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:00,840
Even more.

165
00:10:02,759 --> 00:10:03,399
Against the Yangzhou Team,

166
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,440
the boys fought hard.

167
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:08,639
I saw it all.

168
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,840
We just lacked a bit of luck.

169
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,759
There are eight matches left.

170
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:14,480
As long as we give it our all,

171
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:17,480
we'll score more goals

172
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,159
and win back our pride.

173
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,799
These two hundred bucks,

174
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:26,840
I'll take them.

175
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,279
I'll make another bet with you.

176
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:29,879
In the upcoming matches,

177
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,360
we'll score just the same.

178
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:32,679
Only this time the ball

179
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,720
will slam into the opponent's net!

180
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,480
I believe you.

181
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,799
I'm not betting against you anymore.

182
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:45,240
At least the first valid goal

183
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:47,559
was scored by me, right?

184
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:49,799
Am I right?

185
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:52,240
Losing one match isn't scary.

186
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:53,759
What's scary is

187
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:55,799
not giving our all, not fighting.

188
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,440
As long as we go all out,

189
00:10:58,519 --> 00:10:59,639
it'll be the greatest encouragement

190
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:00,639
to this city.

191
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,559
Don't carry any baggage.

192
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:03,720
Throw that baggage away!

193
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,960
The sky won't fall.

194
00:11:05,639 --> 00:11:07,120
What we really need right now

195
00:11:09,399 --> 00:11:10,480
is just one goal.

196
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:11,960
Just one single goal

197
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:15,000
can lift this entire city's

198
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,480
confidence.

199
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:21,600
I got some news.

200
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:23,639
The Jiangsu Super League right now

201
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,399
is taking the whole country by storm.

202
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:27,440
The officials are taking it very seriously.

203
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,240
The next match

204
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,240
will be moved to

205
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,960
the Olympic Center Stadium.

206
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,000
This is a national-level

207
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,679
match.

208
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,120
We've been gelling until now,

209
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:41,360
and getting better and better.

210
00:11:42,279 --> 00:11:42,919
I believe

211
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:44,519
our first victory

212
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,360
will come very soon.

213
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:49,000
Perform your best.

214
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,399
Do right by ourselves.

215
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:53,720
For our first victory!

216
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,159
Every upcoming match,

217
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:57,679
every training session,

218
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,120
we must all

219
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,799
truly cherish.

220
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:02,919
Let's go, everyone!

221
00:12:05,759 --> 00:12:06,200
Yeah!

222
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,639
Changzhou FC has gone

223
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,399
totally viral online.

224
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:19,399
The trending list

225
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:20,440
is completely blowing up.

226
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:21,840
This massive wave of traffic,

227
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:22,960
we've got to seize it.

228
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,320
So, everyone,

229
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,120
hurry up and

230
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:26,759
gather up all the memes online.

231
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:28,440
Bad publicity is still publicity.

232
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:29,159
Also,

233
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,840
we need to create some buzz,

234
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,840
ride this wave of public entertainment,

235
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:33,840
and roast ourselves.

236
00:12:34,159 --> 00:12:35,159
Honestly, after filming this far,

237
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,679
we kind of feel sorry for them.

238
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:37,360
Look,

239
00:12:37,639 --> 00:12:39,440
if some social media outlets

240
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:41,000
are pushing hate content,

241
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,840
then shouldn't we

242
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,720
do something deeper and uplifting?

243
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:47,679
You've become a fan

244
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,279
this quickly?

245
00:12:50,039 --> 00:12:50,639
But,

246
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,840
how are we supposed to encourage them?

247
00:12:53,399 --> 00:12:54,720
There's absolutely no hope.

248
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,279
They can't even beat the Yangzhou Team.

249
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:57,639
We might as well join everyone

250
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:58,360
in having some fun.

251
00:12:59,039 --> 00:13:00,120
It's just a friendly match anyway.

252
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:01,399
Win or lose doesn't matter.

253
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:02,879
Traffic is king.

254
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:03,879
Director,

255
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:05,120
don't you think this wave of traffic

256
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,360
is kind of strange?

257
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:08,600
Aren't we at the bottom of the rankings,

258
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:09,440
without scoring a single goal?

259
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:10,399
Then why

260
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,519
are there still so many netizens

261
00:13:11,919 --> 00:13:13,480
who love and support Changzhou FC?

262
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,399
Why does Changzhou FC currently have

263
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,360
the most memes about them?

264
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,279
Isn't it because

265
00:13:18,759 --> 00:13:19,720
they're the most ordinary,

266
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,799
yet most desperate for a win?

267
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,639
That's an interesting angle.

268
00:13:26,399 --> 00:13:26,720
Alright.

269
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:27,639
Here's what we'll do.

270
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,080
You go do a series of reports.

271
00:13:29,559 --> 00:13:30,720
Just answer one question for me.

272
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,440
They're the most ordinary,

273
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,720
but how exactly are they ordinary?

274
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:34,879
They fight the hardest,

275
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,120
but how exactly do they fight?

276
00:13:36,759 --> 00:13:37,440
Why is everyone

277
00:13:37,759 --> 00:13:38,919
ignoring professional matches

278
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:40,679
to watch our amateur Jiangsu Super League?

279
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:42,440
Why does everyone support

280
00:13:42,799 --> 00:13:43,919
not the first-place team,

281
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,480
but Changzhou FC at the bottom?

282
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:00,600
Hello?

283
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:01,720
Hi there.

284
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:03,240
I'm Lü Qingqing, a reporter.

285
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,080
We're working on a story

286
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,519
about Changzhou FC.

287
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,000
How many times do I have to say it?

288
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,399
I don't do interviews.

289
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:10,440
Please don't call

290
00:14:10,519 --> 00:14:11,200
this number again.

291
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,080
Hanging up.

292
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:15,200
Was that the Lü Qingqing woman?

293
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,919
She's so persistent, insisting on an interview.

294
00:14:19,039 --> 00:14:19,799
Our team, man,

295
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,399
we're trending online

296
00:14:21,559 --> 00:14:22,440
like crazy right now.

297
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:23,840
We're honestly

298
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,120
getting famous for all the wrong reasons.

299
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,759
They're just chasing clout.

300
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,559
She's driving me nuts.

301
00:14:28,799 --> 00:14:29,639
She even called up

302
00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:30,720
our school to reach me.

303
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:31,600
She got my dad's number

304
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,639
straight from the school.

305
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,279
I gotta say, she's pretty impressive.

306
00:14:34,559 --> 00:14:35,679
Going all the way to the school.

307
00:14:37,559 --> 00:14:38,039
You ready yet?

308
00:14:38,679 --> 00:14:39,080
Let's go eat.

309
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:39,600
Come on.

310
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:40,639
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

311
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:41,639
I haven't washed up yet.

312
00:14:41,639 --> 00:14:42,799
Wait for me, you guys.

313
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:43,960
Wait for you?

314
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,200
The food'll be stone cold by then.

315
00:14:45,759 --> 00:14:46,480
I'll be right there!

316
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,639
I'm fine with anything.

317
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,120
Go on in and wait for me.

318
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:57,720
Alright.

319
00:14:57,919 --> 00:14:58,840
Let's go.

320
00:15:07,039 --> 00:15:08,200
Why aren't you answering my calls?

321
00:15:08,639 --> 00:15:09,519
And the door's bolted from inside.

322
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:10,240
What's that supposed to mean?

323
00:15:15,799 --> 00:15:16,919
Didn't I already tell you?

324
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,200
I want to be alone for a bit.

325
00:15:18,679 --> 00:15:19,519
You always do this.

326
00:15:20,639 --> 00:15:21,600
Whenever something happens,

327
00:15:21,639 --> 00:15:22,399
you just hide away.

328
00:15:23,039 --> 00:15:24,480
Does running away solve anything?

329
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:35,679
Xiaoyong.

330
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,759
We share a life together.

331
00:15:39,879 --> 00:15:41,320
You're not alone in this.

332
00:15:41,559 --> 00:15:42,559
Why can't you just...

333
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,799
be like everyone else?

334
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,840
If something's wrong, tell me.

335
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,360
I can face it

336
00:15:47,399 --> 00:15:48,480
together with you.

337
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:55,799
Don't be like this.

338
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,320
Everyone's watching.

339
00:15:58,279 --> 00:15:59,120
Don't give them something to laugh at.

340
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:00,679
I'm going inside.

341
00:16:03,399 --> 00:16:04,799
Then let them laugh at me.

342
00:16:04,879 --> 00:16:05,240
Right?

343
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:07,360
Yeah.

344
00:16:08,279 --> 00:16:09,399
I'm nothing but a joke.

345
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,279
I've been dating you

346
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,240
for all these years,

347
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:13,720
and I haven't even given you

348
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:14,480
the most basic commitment.

349
00:16:15,159 --> 00:16:16,440
The moment something happens,

350
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:17,840
you just disappear.

351
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:18,919
Xiaoyong,

352
00:16:19,399 --> 00:16:20,840
we're a couple.

353
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,600
I mean less to you than your friends.

354
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,720
I'm just in the way.

355
00:16:24,799 --> 00:16:25,679
My dad was right.

356
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,120
Your dad was right.

357
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:28,720
Your dad wasn't wrong.

358
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,039
I'm a useless person,

359
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,399
a person with no sense of responsibility.

360
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:37,600
Li Xiaoyong,

361
00:16:38,679 --> 00:16:40,480
don't mistake my kindness for malice.

362
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:48,879
Lu Yao,

363
00:16:51,159 --> 00:16:52,320
I don't have a single cent in savings.

364
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,600
I'm almost thirty years old.

365
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,120
I have no career,

366
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:57,240
no stable job.

367
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,320
What can I possibly promise you?

368
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,240
The only thing I could control, football,

369
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,359
with the whole internet watching,

370
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,400
I humiliated myself like that.

371
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,039
I'm just a useless person.

372
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,240
I don't need your concern.

373
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,240
I... I'm thankful to you.

374
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:15,480
I really appreciate you.

375
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:17,319
And I appreciate your dad's kindness too.

376
00:17:17,359 --> 00:17:18,000
But I don't need him

377
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:19,240
to give me a job like that.

378
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:24,000
The only thing I want to do right now

379
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,759
is to quietly

380
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,759
finish the matches.

381
00:17:29,359 --> 00:17:30,200
That's what I currently think

382
00:17:30,279 --> 00:17:31,039
is the most important thing.

383
00:17:31,119 --> 00:17:31,799
Do you understand?

384
00:17:39,759 --> 00:17:40,119
Fine.

385
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:43,000
Since you think I'm not important,

386
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:45,720
and you're telling me not to contact you,

387
00:17:49,599 --> 00:17:50,319
then from now on,

388
00:17:50,319 --> 00:17:51,359
let's never contact each other again.
